        "responses": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=Summarize this email in exactly 4 sections with these headers:\n\n🎯 The Pitch\n\nWho emailed and what do they want? Keep it to 1-2 sentences maximum.\n\nStart casually, like:\n\n\"Hey! Arjun just slid into your inbox about [topic].\"\n\n---\n\n📋 The Details\n\nExplain the main proposal, request, issue, or important facts in a conversational way.\n\nKeep it to 2-3 sentences maximum.\n\n---\n\n⏰ The Timeline\n\nMention any dates, deadlines, meetings, or time-sensitive information.\n\nIf there is no timeline, write exactly:\n\n\"No specific timeline—just a heads up.\"\n\n---\n\n🚨 Priority Level\n\nAssign ONLY one priority:\n\n* High\n* Medium\n* Low\n\nRules:\n\n* High → Urgent emails, deadlines, work requests, client communications, action required.\n* Medium → Important updates or follow-ups that are not urgent.\n* Low → Newsletters, marketing emails, promotions, social notifications, advertisements.\n\nAfter the priority, add one short sentence explaining why.\n\nExample:\n\nMedium – Important information, but no immediate action is required.\n\n---\n\nEMAIL TO SUMMARIZE:\n\nSender Email: {{ $json.From }}\n\nSubject: {{ $json.Subject }}\n\nContent: {{ $json.snippet }}\n\n---\n\nKeep the tone short, casual, and conversational.\n\nDo not add anything outside these four sections.\n"
            },
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "You're an intelligent email assistant "
            }
          ]
        },
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {}
      },
